data.description: This three bedroom, two bath updated home sits on just over one acre with beautiful views of the sunrise from the front porch. Enjoy plenty of living space in the living room as well as a separate family room with wood burning fireplace and access to the back deck and flat backyard. Spacious primary bedroom and updated bathroom with two vanities, clawfoot tub and shower. Built-in pantry/cabinet in dining area and linen closet in the hall bathroom. There is a garden shed too. All conveniently located to Roanoke, Christiansburg and Floyd. Call for a private showing today!
